msgctxt "an4.264:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.264:0.2"
msgid "27. Kammapathavagga"
msgstr "27. Ways of Performing Deeds"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: pāṇātipātasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.264:0.3"
msgid "264. Pāṇātipātīsutta"
msgstr "264. Killing Living Creatures"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.264:1.1"
msgid "“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr "“Mendicants, someone with four qualities is cast down to hell."

msgctxt "an4.264:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.264:1.3"
msgid "Attanā ca pāṇātipātī hoti, parañca pāṇātipāte samādapeti, pāṇātipāte ca samanuñño hoti, pāṇātipātassa ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati—"
msgstr "They themselves kill living creatures; they encourage others to kill living creatures; they approve of killing living creatures; and they praise killing living creatures."

msgctxt "an4.264:1.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr "Someone with these four qualities is cast down to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.264:2.1"
msgid "Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge."
msgstr "Someone with four qualities is raised up to heaven."

msgctxt "an4.264:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.264:2.3"
msgid "Attanā ca pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, parañca pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā samādapeti, pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti, pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati—"
msgstr "They don’t themselves kill living creatures; they encourage others to not kill living creatures; they approve of not killing living creatures; and they praise not killing living creatures."

msgctxt "an4.264:2.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge”ti."
msgstr "Someone with these four qualities is raised up to heaven.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.264:2.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
